  candidate to name one packet class, one finite window, one threshold
  language, and one canonical sign / amplitude / phase sheet before arguing
  about usefulness.

## Caution

- A pro-near-circuit-friendly behavioral candidate is honest only if it is
  written in exact projected channel data. As soon as it imports Tao's averaged
  coefficients directly, it stops being a real exact-NS object.

